Package idlreasonerchoco.mapper

Class OASMapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • idlreasonerchoco.mapper.Mapper
      • idlreasonerchoco.mapper.OASMapper
  • public class OASMapper
extends Mapper
    OASMapper class extends Mapper class. This class initializes a configuration object and based on that it reads and generates IDL from open API specification. Also,it has an OASSolver object as a member which is used to do the following:
    • To use choco model.
    • To map string to integer value.
    • To get map of variables.
    • To restart the solver.
    See Also:
    OASSolver
